author: bluelion3
title: Very fun Duplo--car, food, and cat!
review:
My son loves this set! 

He has about six or seven Duplo figures, but the girl with the magenta hoodie is his favorite.

There are some great pieces in this set.  The corn, apples, and oranges fit in the crates and a crate fits inside the van. 

The van is fantastic and even the cat can drive it. 

We use the cash register as a computer and make it say "beep beep beep". 

There is a 2 x 2 Duplo block with a nice strawberry print. 

As with most Duplo sets, these are blended in with the rest of his sets, but these pieces are standouts. 

This is definitely one of the better Duplo sets.
